OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FThe new film called Joy tells the
OL,7,Fastonishing story of how the three
OL,8,Fpioneers of IVF battled widespread
OL,9,Fopposition, ITV News Arts Editor Nina
OL,10,FNannar reports
OL,12,FMeeting Louise Joy Brown in person
OL,13,Fcertainly gives you a moment to pause.
OL,14,FYou are shaking hands with history,
OL,15,Fthe first IVF baby.
