OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FIn 1978, newspaper headlines dubbed
OL,7,Fher the first test tube baby. It
OL,8,Fwasn't a test tube but a bottle called
OL,9,Fa desiccator that was used but hey ho,
OL,10,Ftest tube is a good headline that
OL,11,Fstuck.
OL,13,FLouise is supporting a new film called
OL,14,FJoy which tells the astonishing story
OL,15,Fof how the three pioneers of IVF
OL,16,Fbattled widespread opposition, not
OL,17,Fleast from religious groups, in their
OL,18,Ften-year medical journey to figure out
OL,19,Fhow to fertilise an egg outside the
OL,20,Fmother's body and then implant it into
OL,21,Fthe womb.
