OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FIt is a tale of determination in the
OL,7,Fmidst of huge obstacles and when I met
OL,8,FLouise at Bourn Hall in Cambridge -
OL,9,Fwhich surgeon and gynaecologist
OL,10,FPatrick Steptoe, scientist Bob Edwards
OL,11,Fand embryologist Jean Purdy set up in
OL,12,F1980 - you could see the pride in her
OL,13,Fface.
OL,15,FShe has since lost her parents John
OL,16,Fand Lesley, who made history with her
OL,17,Fall those decades ago, but stresses
OL,18,Fhow the IVF treatment gave the couple
OL,19,Fso much in their lifetime.
