OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FThey were working-class people she
OL,7,Fsays, part of the reason they were
OL,8,Fchosen for the treatment, and that IVF
OL,9,Fon the NHS today is often difficult to
OL,10,Faccess, with rises in waiting times
OL,11,Ffor gynaecological appointments, more
OL,12,Fpeople seeking private treatment, and
OL,13,Fpaying widely different amounts
OL,14,Faccording to where they live.
OL,16,FThe writers, Jack Thorne and his wife
OL,17,FRachel Mason, went through seven
OL,18,Frounds of IVF before their son was
OL,19,Fborn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
