OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FThey say it is not taken seriously
OL,7,Fenough arguing that people who have
OL,8,Fdifficulties conceiving have a right
OL,9,Fto access NHS medical treatment.
OL,10,FInstead, IVF is seen as a luxury -
OL,11,Feven a middle-class pursuit.
OL,13,FRachel quotes a recent report on the
OL,14,Fnumber of PTSD cases following failed
OL,15,FIVF courses.
