OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FIf the film seeks to give the whole
OL,7,Fpicture about the struggles involved
OL,8,Fin bringing IVF into creation, it also
OL,9,Faims to right the wrong that was
OL,10,Fhistorically done against Jean Purdy -
OL,11,Fthe world's first embryologist who has
OL,12,Flargely been written out of history in
OL,13,Fthe story of IVF.
OL,15,FShe died at age 39, without any
OL,16,Fchildren of her own, from cancer and
OL,17,Fvery little was subsequently written
OL,18,Fby her because the cast says she was a
OL,19,Fwoman in what was then a very male
OL,20,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
