OL,3,CFirst IVF baby speaks about new film
OL,4,C'Joy' centred on her miraculous birth
OL,6,FBill Nighy who plays Patrick Steptoe
OL,7,Fsays he learned that it was even
OL,8,Fregarded as a lesser science for
OL,9,Fsomeone like Steptoe to deal with
OL,10,Fwomen's fertility issues.
OL,12,FAnd so Joy puts the woman in the
OL,13,Fcentre frame. Jean Purdy is seen as a
OL,14,Fforce in helping the many women who
OL,15,Funderwent treatment on the road to
OL,16,FLouise Joy Brown being born; it is
OL,17,Fhoped.
